@startuml class_dependencies
' Revised 2026-05-13: applied audit_23 amendments (UpdateCheckService,
' StartMenuShortcut, UpdateConfirmationWindow, DisplayIdentifierService static)
!include dark-theme.puml
title Service & UI dependency graph (who depends on whom)

skinparam classBackgroundColor<<orchestrator>> $STER_ORCHESTRATOR
skinparam classBackgroundColor<<service>>      $STER_SERVICE
skinparam classBackgroundColor<<ui>>           $STER_UI
skinparam classBackgroundColor<<interop>>      $STER_INTEROP
skinparam classBackgroundColor<<lifecycle>>    $STER_LIFECYCLE

' ----- Process bootstrap / lifecycle -----
class Program                          <<orchestrator>>
class App                              <<orchestrator>>
class TrayIconManager                  <<orchestrator>>
class CrashHandler                     <<lifecycle>>
class SingleInstanceCoordinator        <<lifecycle>>
class DisplayEventManager              <<lifecycle>>

' ----- Services -----
class MonitorService                   <<service>>
class DDCRecoveryService               <<service>>
class MonitorBrightnessRangeProvider   <<service>>
class ProfileManager                   <<service>>
class EnvironmentalCurveService        <<service>>
class NightLightProvider               <<service>>
class GlobalHotkeyService              <<service>>
class DisplayIdentifierService         <<service>> /' static class - see note '/
class StartupManager                   <<service>>
class InstallationService              <<service>>
class AsyncThrottler                   <<service>>
class UpdateCheckService               <<service>>
class StartMenuShortcut                <<service>>

' ----- Helpers / models / theming (treated as services for grouping) -----
class AppSettings                      <<service>>
class AppTheme                         <<service>>
class KnownDisplaysStore               <<service>>
class TrayIconRenderer                 <<service>>
class NightLightIconRenderer           <<service>>
class IconRenderingHelper              <<service>>
class GlyphCatalog                     <<service>>
class SunShifter                       <<service>>
class EnvironmentalCurveSampler        <<service>>

' ----- UI -----
class BrightnessFlyout                 <<ui>>
class SettingsWindow                   <<ui>>
class CurveEditor                      <<ui>>
class MapPickerOverlay                 <<ui>>
class DisplayIdentifierOverlayWindow   <<ui>>
class UninstallerWindow                <<ui>>
class NumericSpinner                   <<ui>>
class WindowDragHelper                 <<ui>>
class UpdateConfirmationWindow         <<ui>>

' ----- Interop -----
interface IDisplayService              <<interop>>
class DisplayService                   <<interop>>
class DDCMonitor                       <<interop>>
class Dxva2                            <<interop>>
class CCD                              <<interop>>
class EDIDParser                       <<interop>>
class NightLightRegistry               <<interop>>
class NightLightSettingsHandler        <<interop>>
class NightLightCloudStore             <<interop>>
class NightLightKelvin                 <<interop>>
class PDBSymbolResolver                <<interop>>

' ===========================================================================
' Process bootstrap
' ===========================================================================

Program --> CrashHandler
Program --> SingleInstanceCoordinator
Program --> App
Program --> InstallationService          : --admin-action install-system

' ===========================================================================
' App composition root
' ===========================================================================

App --> AppSettings
App --> AppTheme
App --> MonitorService
App --> DisplayEventManager
App --> DDCRecoveryService
App --> MonitorBrightnessRangeProvider
App --> ProfileManager
App --> NightLightProvider
App --> GlobalHotkeyService
App --> TrayIconManager
App --> BrightnessFlyout
App --> SettingsWindow
App --> UninstallerWindow                : --uninstall mode
App --> StartupManager
App --> PDBSymbolResolver                : DownloadTimeout
App --> UpdateCheckService               : OnStartup -> StateChanged
UpdateCheckService --> AppSettings       : CheckForUpdatesEnabled /\nUpdateCheckIntervalMinutes /\nUpdateChannel

' ===========================================================================
' Tray icon stack
' ===========================================================================

TrayIconManager --> TrayIconRenderer
TrayIconManager ..> AppTheme
TrayIconRenderer --> AppTheme
TrayIconRenderer --> IconRenderingHelper
TrayIconRenderer --> GlyphCatalog
NightLightIconRenderer --> IconRenderingHelper
NightLightIconRenderer --> GlyphCatalog

' ===========================================================================
' Service-to-service
' ===========================================================================

MonitorService --> IDisplayService
MonitorService --> AppSettings
MonitorService --> AsyncThrottler
MonitorService --> KnownDisplaysStore
DDCRecoveryService --> MonitorService
MonitorBrightnessRangeProvider --> MonitorService
DisplayEventManager --> MonitorService   : Refresh()\n+ short-circuit gate
ProfileManager --> KnownDisplaysStore

' Curve evaluation runs as a service so curves keep driving when the flyout is hidden.
EnvironmentalCurveService --> ProfileManager
EnvironmentalCurveService --> MonitorService     : EnqueueDirectBrightness
EnvironmentalCurveService --> NightLightProvider : SetStrength
EnvironmentalCurveService --> SunShifter         : BuildPreview
EnvironmentalCurveService --> EnvironmentalCurveSampler

' Night-light facade fans out to whichever backend is resolved.
NightLightProvider --> AppSettings
NightLightProvider --> NightLightRegistry
NightLightProvider --> NightLightSettingsHandler

' ===========================================================================
' Interop
' ===========================================================================

DisplayService ..|> IDisplayService
DisplayService --> Dxva2
DisplayService --> CCD
DisplayService --> EDIDParser
DisplayService --> DDCMonitor

NightLightSettingsHandler --> NightLightRegistry
NightLightSettingsHandler --> NightLightCloudStore
NightLightSettingsHandler --> NightLightKelvin
NightLightRegistry --> NightLightKelvin
NightLightRegistry --> AsyncThrottler
NightLightCloudStore --> PDBSymbolResolver       : RVA fallback

' ===========================================================================
' UI -> services
' ===========================================================================

BrightnessFlyout --> ProfileManager
BrightnessFlyout --> MonitorService
BrightnessFlyout --> EnvironmentalCurveService
BrightnessFlyout --> NightLightProvider
BrightnessFlyout --> NightLightIconRenderer
BrightnessFlyout --> AppTheme
BrightnessFlyout *-- WindowDragHelper
BrightnessFlyout --> UpdateCheckService          : reads AvailableUpdate /\nNotifyUpdateStateChanged
BrightnessFlyout *-- UpdateConfirmationWindow    : modal child on\nRequestUpdatePrompt

SettingsWindow --> AppSettings
SettingsWindow --> ProfileManager
SettingsWindow --> MonitorService
SettingsWindow --> NightLightProvider
SettingsWindow --> MonitorBrightnessRangeProvider
SettingsWindow --> DisplayIdentifierService
SettingsWindow --> StartupManager
SettingsWindow --> InstallationService
SettingsWindow *-- CurveEditor
SettingsWindow *-- MapPickerOverlay

CurveEditor --> EnvironmentalCurveSampler
CurveEditor --> ProfileManager
CurveEditor --> MonitorBrightnessRangeProvider

' DisplayIdentifierService is a static class that manages a private list
' of overlay windows internally (DisplayIdentifierService.cs:13, 18).
DisplayIdentifierService ..> DisplayIdentifierOverlayWindow : owns N (one per monitor)
UninstallerWindow --> InstallationService

' StartMenuShortcut wiring (cf410f7: Start Menu shortcuts).
Program --> StartMenuShortcut            : --admin-action sync-startmenu
InstallationService --> StartMenuShortcut : Sync()
StartupManager --> StartMenuShortcut     : RepairShortcutIfStale

' ===========================================================================
' Notes
' ===========================================================================

note right of MonitorService
  Internal clusters:
    A enumeration / reconciliation
    B brightness I/O via AsyncThrottler
      (write -> retry -> verify)
    C sorting & overrides
    D recovery coordination
    E shutdown drain
end note

note bottom of BrightnessFlyout
  Curve evaluation lives in
  EnvironmentalCurveService;
  flyout is an observer.
end note

note bottom of SettingsWindow
  Per-tab pages in WPF/Settings/Pages/*.
  CurveEditor + MapPickerOverlay are
  hosted directly by the shell so the
  preview sweep can dock either one.
end note

note top of DisplayEventManager
  Single message-only HWND;
  owns the WM_DEVICECHANGE pipeline,
  fast-path debounce + slow-path
  SetupAPI burst.
end note

note bottom of NightLightProvider
  Backend resolved lazily:
  Registry (CloudStore Bond blob) or
  SettingsHandler (kelvin via RVA into
  SettingsHandlers_Display.dll).
end note

@enduml
